item.title: Meet Eric
item.description: Eric's Lincoln Story As a native Lincolnite, business owner, software engineer, property owner, teacher, mentor, lifelong learner, and parent, I am the different kind of leader we need in Lincoln. Meet Eric Hi, I'm Eric. I'm a 36 year old Lincoln, Nebraskan. I've lived here my entire life--in fact, I live a block from where I grew up.
